                   on the King's highway, on the <rs id="t17860222-121-cd605" type="crimeDate">11th day of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17860222-121-off604 t17860222-121-cd605"></join> last, and putting him in corporal fear and danger of his life, and feloniously taking from his person, and against his will, a boy's suit of clothes, value 5 s. the property of 
                     <persName id="t17860222-121-person1182">
                        William
                         Shakespear
                     <interp inst="t17860222-121-person1182" type="surname" value="Shakespear"></interp>
